description:
On Today's Episode of the Dan Patrick Show DP recaps last night's NBA Action. Will there be any parody on the Eastern Conference side in Round 2? Quarterback Guru/Former NFL QB Jordan Palmer and NBA HOF/Turner Sports Analyst Reggie Miller join us. Plus, DP makes a bet against the Danettes with a couple Pies to the face on the line.
